    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure! If you're looking for something reliable that still looks great on the road, this is definitely the one for you. It runs smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
