    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example boasts a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent VANOS service and valve adjustment, ensuring the high-pressure VANOS system operates within spec. While showing signs of spirited use, the mechanical integrity is robust, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
