    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish that shines beautifully in the sun; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving, the body remains straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort. The premium leather upholstery is supple and clean, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and the interior is entirely smoke-free. All technological features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been serviced at regular intervals; the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. The tires have ample tread remaining, ensuring you are ready for the road ahead. This is a solid, reliable car that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
