      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained to ensure peak performance and long-term reliability. It boasts a refined interior and a clean, well-preserved exterior, reflecting a history of responsible ownership. Having passed our comprehensive technical evaluation, this unit offers a sophisticated driving experience and remains a premier choice for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-caliber vehicle.",
