      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been so reliable for me and is still in really solid shape, both inside and out! It drives like a dream and has been well-loved and looked after. If you're looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure, this is the one. Feel free to message me with any questions\u2014I'd love for you to come see it in person!",
